</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Thomas Merton bibliography</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Thomas_Merton_hermitage_interior_(Abbey_of_Gethsemani).jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Thomas_Merton_hermitage_interior_%28Abbey_of_Gethsemani%29.jpg/250px-Thomas_Merton_hermitage_interior_%28Abbey_of_Gethsemani%29.jpg" width="250" height="188" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Thomas_Merton_hermitage_interior_%28Abbey_of_Gethsemani%29.jpg/375px-Thomas_Merton_hermitage_interior_%28Abbey_of_Gethsemani%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Thomas_Merton_hermitage_interior_%28Abbey_of_Gethsemani%29.jpg/500px-Thomas_Merton_hermitage_interior_%28Abbey_of_Gethsemani%29.jpg 2x" data-file-width="800" data-file-height="600" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Thomas_Merton_hermitage_interior_(Abbey_of_Gethsemani).jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>
Thomas Merton's hermitage (interior) at the Abbey of Gethsemani</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Below is a bibliography of published works written by <a href="/wiki/Thomas_Merton" title="Thomas Merton">Thomas Merton</a>, the <a href="/wiki/Trappist" title="Trappist" class="mw-redirect">Trappist</a> monk of <a href="/wiki/The_Abbey_of_Our_Lady_of_Gethsemani" title="The Abbey of Our Lady of Gethsemani" class="mw-redirect">The Abbey of Our Lady of Gethsemani</a>. Several of the works listed here have been published posthumously. The works are listed under each category by date of publication.</p>
<p></p>
