<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Contemplation_and_meditations">Contemplation and meditations</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Thomas_Merton_bibliography&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Contemplation and meditations">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li><span class="citation book"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/225115&amp;referer=brief_results"><i>Seeds of Contemplation</i></a>. New Directions. 1949. <a href="/wiki/OCLC" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.worldcat.org/oclc/225115">225115</a>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThomas+Merton+bibliography&amp;rft.btitle=Seeds+of+Contemplation&amp;rft.date=1949&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldcat.org%2Foclc%2F225115%26referer%3Dbrief_results&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F225115&amp;rft.pub=New+Directions&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
